[normal]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Supplementary[bold] written evidence [bold]from RMT ([bold]TIC [bold]091A)[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Bus services in rural areas[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Key points[bold]&#xa0;
